    <briefdescription>
<para>Container for GPIO pin information specified in devicetree. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This type contains a pointer to a GPIO device, pin number for a pin controlled by that device, and the subset of pin configuration flags which may be given in devicetree.</para>
